						.icon.bg-primary-light.rounded-lg.mb-4.p-2
							img(alt='Icon' src='/images/icons/primary/layers-3.svg', height='48')
						h5.mb-3 Free updates
						p.lead.mx-2 If you want to add a bit of noise in your design, so it did not look too boring, you can use ready-made dot background system or make your own background with Figma file, which is also included


		// CONTENT
		#content.bg-light.border-top.border-bottom(data-aos="fade")
			.container
				.row
					.col-lg-5.col-md-12.my-auto.mr-auto.pt-8.pb-5
						.mb-3.initialism.text-primary Killer features
						p.lead.mb-4.mr-8
							| Replacer is constantly growing and updatable teme, and we have long-term plans to making it better
						.row.mb-3
							.col
								.mb-2
									span.display-4.text-dark.mr-2 320
									span.initialism.text-muted gb
								p.text-muted If you want to add a bit of noise in your design, so it did not look too boring, you can use ready-made dot background system or make your own background with Figma file, which is also included
							.col
								.mb-2
									span.display-4.text-dark.mr-2 2.4
									span.initialism.text-muted millions
								p.text-muted If you want to add a bit of noise in your design, so it did not look too boring, you can use ready-made dot background system or make your own background with Figma file, which is also included
					.col-lg-6.col-md-12.my-auto
						img.w-100(alt='Illustration' src='/images/illustrations/illustration_9.png')


		// LEAD
		#lead_section(data-aos="fade")
			.container.py-10.jarallax(style="background: url('/images/bg/bg_05.svg') center center no-repeat;")
				.row.text-center
					.col-lg-7.col-md-12.col-sm-12.mx-auto
						.icon.bg-primary-light.rounded-lg.mb-5.p-2
							img(alt='Icon' src='/images/icons/primary/cursor-click-2.svg', height='48')
						h5.mb-3 Content-oriented design
						p.lead.mb-5.mx-0.mx-md-6.mx-lg-8 Replacer is a perfect tool to start making landing pages with Bootstrap 4. We provide content-oriented, clean, and mobile-first layouts, which you can easily customize for your needs. Here are some carefully designed demos, use it out of the box or customize the way you want
						a.btn-link.text-primary.hvr-icon-forward(href="/pages/page-apply.html")
							| Request a demo
							small
								i.fas.fa-chevron-right.ml-2.hvr-icon

		
		// SPLIT
		#split.bg-light.border-top.border-bottom.py-4
			.container
				.row.my-auto
					
					.col-lg-5.col-md-12.col-sm-12.my-auto.py-8.mr-auto(data-aos="fade")
						.initialism.mb-4.text-muted Demo video
						h5.mb-2 Power of good design
						p.lead.mb-5.mr-5 Replacer is a perfect tool to start making landing pages with Bootstrap 4. We provide content-oriented, clean, and mobile-first layouts, which you can easily customize for your needs. Here are some carefully designed demos, use it out of the box or customize the way you want. We also made illustrations and line icons, lorem ipsum dolor set amet
						hr.mb-4
						a.btn-link.text-primary.hvr-icon-forward(href="/pages/page-apply.html")
							| Request a demo
							small
								i.fas.fa-chevron-right.ml-2.hvr-icon


					.col-lg-6.col-md-12.col-sm-12.my-auto(data-aos="fade-left")
						.carousel-1-arrows.arrows-white
							.card.rounded-lg.overflow-hidden.border-0
								img.w-100(alt='Slide' src='/images/photos/slide3.jpg')
							.card.rounded-lg.overflow-hidden.border-0
								img.w-100(alt='Slide' src='/images/photos/slide2.jpg')
							.card.rounded-lg.overflow-hidden.border-0
								img.w-100(alt='Slide' src='/images/photos/slide1.jpg')


		// FORM
		#form
			.container.pt-11.pb-11.jarallax(style="background: url('/images/bg/bg_03.svg') center center;")
				.row(data-aos="fade")
					.col-lg-9.mx-auto.text-center
						.mb-3.text-muted.initialism Free registration
						h5.display-3.mb-3 Create an account
						p.lead.mx-0.mx-lg-15.pb-4
							| If you want to add a bit of noise in your design, so it did not look too boring, you can use ready-made dot background system or make your own background with attached Figma file
						form.mb-4
							.form-row
								.input-group.col-lg-4.mb-3
									input.form-control.rounded.mx-0(type='text', placeholder="Email", aria-label="Email")
								.input-group.col-lg-4.mb-3
									input.form-control.rounded.mx-0.mx-lg-1.mx-xl-1(type='password', placeholder="Password", aria-label="Password")
								.input-group.col-lg-4.mb-3
									button.btn.btn-primary.w-100(type='button') Get started
										i.fas.fa-arrow-right.ml-2.small
						p.mt-2.mb-5.mb-0.small.text-muted.text-center
							i.fas.fa-check-circle.mr-2
							span Your personal data is safe with us 
						.mx-auto
							a.btn.btn-outline-facebook.rounded-pill.btn-sm.px-3.mr-2(href='#')
								i.fab.fa-facebook-f.mr-2
								| Continue
							a.icon.btn.btn-outline-twitter.rounded-circle.mr-2(href="#")
								i.fab.fa-twitter
							a.icon.btn.btn-outline-google.rounded-circle(href="#")
								i.fab.fa-google


